<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Khrihfa, i ralring u, rawhnak a nai, Lung a dermi le ral a chiami hna,
 Khual nan tlawn lioah, Ther le phan pah in, Nanmah nan rawh nakhnga
 sualnak a tam. Khrihfa i ralring u, Khrihfa i ralring u, Khrihfa i
 ralring u, rawhnak a nai.

[V2]
 Khrihfa, nan lung fek u, thli a hrang lai, Khua nih a fakpi in dawm
 hmanhsehlaw, Khuadawmnak le thlitu a tian zaulai, Khamhbawi sinah a
 zungzal nan um lai. Khrihfa lawm in kal u, Khrihfa lawm in kal u, Khrihfa
 lawm in kal u, thlihran zongah,

[V3]
 Khrihfa, thlacam tuah u, lampalh a fawi, Nan Bawi nih an auhnak kha
 zum ko u, Nan Khamhbawi sinah thla nan cam ahcun, Tukforh le hneksaknak
 nan tei khawh lai. Khrihfa thlacam tuah u, Khrihfa thlacam tuah u,
 Khrihfa thlacam tuah u, lam palh a fawi.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>KHRIHFA I RALRING U CH282</title>
<hymn_number>282</hymn_number>
</song>